[[File:Liftclaw.jpg|thumb|right|250px| A lift claw in [[Kaerobani's base]]]]
'''Lifting claws''' were a type of device used to move cargo from place to place within buildings. They were often employed in [[Hangar/Legends|docking bays]], and could be used to store various [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]]. Certain examples ran on straight tracks mounted high on walls, while others were fixed in position. They were imployed in [[Kaerobani's base]] in [[10 ABY/Legends|10 ABY]], as well as his orbiting shipyards and the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] base on [[Altyr V]].<ref name="MoS">''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith]]''</ref> Smaller versions were installed on [[Telgorn Corporation/Legends|Telgorn Corporation's]] [[Mark VI Powersuit]],<ref name="EJ">{{WEGCite|story=The Evacuation of Jatee|book=Supernova (sourcebook)}}</ref> [[Serv-O-Droid, Inc.]]'s [[DC5-1]] [[Loader droid/Legends|freight droid]],<ref name="HSCS">''[[Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook]]''</ref> and [[LesTech]]'s [[PackTrack 41LT-R]].<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

